description: 1911 Gold Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the acquisition, exploration, development, and extraction of precious metals. It primarily explores for gold. The company holds a land package totaling 58,672 hectares within and adjacent to the Archean Rice Lake greenstone belt in Manitoba. It also owns interests in the True North mine and mill complex located in Bissett, Manitoba; and Apex property consisting of 5 mining claims covering an area of approximately 752 hectares located near Snow Lake, Manitoba, as well as in Tully and Denton-Keefer projects located near Timmins, Ontario. The company was formerly known as Havilah Mining Corporation and changed its name to 1911 Gold Corporation in June 2019. 1911 Gold Corporation was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. R. Shaun Heinrichs (Illinois), BBA, CPA, CA, CPA
